{"tid":527994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國「新垣結衣」 靚樣紅到日本 網民:太可愛了","createTime":"2018-01-13T09:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T10:43:19.000Z","uid":25345,"like":61,"dislike":616,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d6156024c69a550bc02adadf41843220193a36","tid":527994,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"日本女星新垣結衣氣質甜美，自從演出日劇《逃跑雖可恥但有用》紅爆後，便被封為日本「國民老婆」。出道10年的她，始終維持凍齡美貌。近日，內地就有一名靚女，因外型酷似新垣結衣，成為網民焦點。<br />\n<br />\n綽號栗子的她本名叫作「龍夢柔」，來自少數民族「土家族」，今年22歲，2014年參加「來吧！灰姑娘」獲得冠軍，有不少網友發現，她的五官和新垣結衣相似度極高，狂被網友誇讚。龍夢柔也喜歡新垣結衣，先前還在IG上模仿新垣結衣跳「戀舞」的影片，被日媒報道後，許多日本粉絲都相當稱讚她，「因為你我決定學中文」、「真的太可愛了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180111/large/1515675805_1e60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180111%2Flarge%2F1515675805_1e60.jpg&h=973af420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180111/large/1515675801_7f68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180111%2Flarge%2F1515675801_7f68.jpg&h=87e4f443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180111/large/1515675803_616b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180111%2Flarge%2F1515675803_616b.jpg&h=b918ecf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180111/large/1515675810_a2bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180111%2Flarge%2F1515675810_a2bc.jpg&h=c07b020f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180111/large/1515675811_b265.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180111%2Flarge%2F1515675811_b265.jpg&h=38f857b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br 